WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:07.999
Hey, good morning, family. How are you all doing today? I have my wife with me again.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:17.782
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, she's not to walk behind you; she's to walk beside you concerning things.'I want her on the broadcast more.

00:00:17.783 --> 00:00:25.554
I want her to come on and talk more. She has a lot inside of her.

00:00:25.555 --> 00:00:34.859
She's been in the background doing emails and things like that, and now we're homeschooling the kids and getting ready for this new school year.

00:00:34.860 --> 00:00:45.679
It's a lot, but there is so much inside of her, and I want to hear more. I'm going to bring her on more and we're going to talk.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:56.905
The Lord told me a couple of days ago—I've had some amazing visitations in the last two weeks.

00:00:56.906 --> 00:01:07.236
The intensity of the river has doubled on my life with the things the Lord is showing me.

00:01:07.237 --> 00:01:14.708
I call it the prophetic pulse. I'm so humbled that He would come and visit me, but it's for you all.

00:01:14.709 --> 00:01:26.039
He instructs me about my own life—things that I can't talk about.

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:38.495
I try to talk about it and people say, 'Well, you're bragging,'so I've realized there are a lot of things I just keep quiet now.

00:01:38.496 --> 00:01:45.080
I'm learning; this whole thing has been like a fire hydrant shot right at me.

00:01:45.081 --> 00:02:01.410
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you can't talk about some of this stuff.'I realized some of the things He's showing me are for me to pray over personally.

00:02:01.411 --> 00:02:21.112
I'm a work in progress. Diana and I are just grabbing on with both fingers and our teeth, saying we're not letting go.

00:02:21.113 --> 00:02:35.054
People want to know how Megan is doing. She's getting better and better. A miracle is a miracle even if it's progressive.

00:02:35.055 --> 00:02:54.809
The doctor said she would stay at the mental capability of a two-and-a-half-year-old for the rest of her life, but we're believing God that we're going up.

00:02:54.810 --> 00:03:17.465
She's come a long way, but we still have a long way to go. For the first time in years, we are able to go to church as a family and not just watch online because of the distraction she had been in public.

00:03:17.466 --> 00:03:31.713
The ushers used to have us leave because she was so disruptive, but now we can sit in the back and pray for the people.

00:03:31.714 --> 00:03:39.774
It's been such a blessing. They're having a prayer conference in Branson, Missouri.

00:03:39.775 --> 00:03:44.618
Sister Billie Brim is going to be having a prayer conference in October.

00:03:44.619 --> 00:03:57.719
I think it would be wonderful if you all support her. The Lord showed me a great move of God coming for that area.

00:03:57.720 --> 00:04:02.554
Great signs and wonders are coming to Branson, Missouri, and the Lord told me it's going to start with Billie Brim.

00:04:02.555 --> 00:04:43.638
I asked, 'Why her, Lord?'and He said, 'Because she asks for it over and over.'I saw a Shekinah Glory cloud, like a thick fog, the presence of the Lord coming in like it did in the Old Testament.

00:04:43.639 --> 00:05:08.653
I saw a glory cloud come in while she's doing prayer. I anticipate it every time.

00:05:08.654 --> 00:05:22.673
It will be birthed out of love and prayer. They will have a major move of God.

00:05:22.674 --> 00:05:33.927
I saw a glory cloud coming in and people being healed when that presence of the Lord comes into that auditorium.

00:05:33.928 --> 00:05:52.785
Everyone will be healed in that service—nothing missing, nothing broken, Shalom. It's time for an outpouring like we've never seen before.

00:05:52.786 --> 00:06:13.739
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you need to talk about the things that I'm going to do and the glorious outpouring.'He told me to inspire His people and go back to the basics—to teach prayer and the Word.

00:06:13.740 --> 00:06:47.959
That's the balance. You have to have the Word as a balance; it's like a teeter-totter that keeps you from getting off into weirdo land.

00:06:47.960 --> 00:07:00.851
We want to follow the Holy Spirit in our lives and ministry. The bottom line is teaching you how to stand by faith and pray in the Spirit.

00:07:00.852 --> 00:07:22.404
If you don't pray in tongues, you're missing out. Praying in the Spirit stirs yourself up.

00:07:22.405 --> 00:07:42.577
Diana and I keep going despite the waves that have knocked us down over the years.

00:07:42.578 --> 00:08:03.948
We will serve the Lord, fighting the good fight of faith and standing on the Word as Holy Ghost-filled Christians who will not compromise.

00:08:03.949 --> 00:08:18.798
We will not bend our knee to Baal. I met Diana at Jeremy Pearsons'Bible study.

00:08:18.799 --> 00:08:34.395
We've been together since she was 15 and married for over 20 years.

00:08:34.396 --> 00:08:39.962
We've stayed together through everything because of prayer and love.

00:08:39.963 --> 00:09:01.239
I can be a rascal and I'm not always easy to be with, but we're going to make it.

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:26.361
For those of you who are weary because you aren't seeing your manifestation, I want to inspire you to keep on keeping on.

00:09:26.362 --> 00:09:43.651
Stand therefore. What keeps us going is the Word of God and finding books that fan that flame.

00:09:43.652 --> 00:09:58.046
I love the book *The Man Who Talks with the Flowers* about George Washington Carver.

00:09:58.047 --> 00:10:06.883
It's an older book by Glenn Clark. Carver's relationship with the Lord inspires me.

00:10:06.884 --> 00:10:09.003
Because I have learning disabilities and don't read well, Diana reads to me.

00:10:09.004 --> 00:11:58.376
She reads at least 50 books a year. The simplicity of his relationship with God is beautiful.

00:11:58.377 --> 00:12:42.080
It doesn't have to be complicated; we should come to God like a child. What fans your flame?

00:12:42.081 --> 00:12:54.021
For me, it's books like this and the healing testimonies of Azusa Street.

00:12:54.022 --> 00:13:04.470
I've been reading *True Stories of the Miracles of Azusa Street*.

00:13:04.471 --> 00:13:34.994
If He did it once, He'll do it again. God is no respecter of persons. I've seen a great revival and that glory cloud coming.

00:13:34.995 --> 00:14:56.933
One last call: if you truly realize how much Jesus loves you—He oozes love. Being touched by the Father changes you and makes you soft.

00:14:56.934 --> 00:15:29.833
Two nights ago, I was on a ladder putting a new light up, and the presence of the Lord hit me so hard I had to get down.

00:15:29.834 --> 00:15:43.916
I saw again what's coming: I saw the devil and all the principalities and legions behind him.

00:15:43.917 --> 00:15:50.772
They were at attention, looking at the Father, knowing their time was up.

00:15:50.773 --> 00:16:30.799
The light from the Father's throne was blinding. I saw Satan cowered down, hunkered toward the ground.

00:16:30.800 --> 00:16:56.670
He knew the sun had set on humanity. Jesus is coming. If your heart is not right, you're going to get left.

00:16:56.671 --> 00:17:11.921
Get your heart right before the Father right now. If you're walking on the fence, woe unto you.

00:17:11.922 --> 00:17:33.879
Satan was cowering, melting down like a fool because he turned his back on the King of Kings.

00:17:33.880 --> 00:18:10.007
The principalities and powers looked worried. They knew they made the wrong choice by following the devil.

00:18:10.008 --> 00:18:15.368
Every knee will bow and every tongue will confess that Jesus Christ is Lord.

00:18:15.369 --> 00:20:13.641
Even those devils will tremble. We are about to step into our glorified bodies and rule with Him forever.

00:20:13.642 --> 00:20:52.602
I saw a major move of God coming to Hollywood—to A-list celebrities like Justin Bieber. They are hurting and thirsty for more.

00:20:52.603 --> 00:21:37.397
They will have a great influence in bringing others to the kingdom because God will touch even the hardest people.

00:21:37.398 --> 00:21:56.839
I want to read a beautiful testimony about a healing that took place at Azusa Street.

00:21:56.840 --> 00:22:40.163
The Lord told me He wants His people to believe bigger. This story is of a child whose second teeth grew in rotten and black.

00:22:40.164 --> 00:22:53.472
Lucille said, 'God will heal anything.'Lucille laid a handkerchief over the child's mouth and prayed.

00:22:53.473 --> 00:23:58.970
A handful of blackened teeth dropped into a cup. Then new teeth grew in one at a time. The child said it kind of tickled.

00:23:58.971 --> 00:24:16.466
Sister Lucille was a little woman, but she could command a leg to grow or a wrist to heal.

00:24:16.467 --> 00:25:33.200
She described the Shekinah Glory as a mist-like cloud. She would sit in it and play in it, and it was like breathing in pure oxygen.

00:25:33.201 --> 00:26:25.119
The scent was like lilacs or roses. When they would sing in the Spirit, the glory would rise and fill the whole room.

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:40.864
Megan is going to be radically healed like that. I'm expecting it.

00:26:40.865 --> 00:26:59.582
It will be a sign to the world that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:26:59.583 --> 00:27:39.215
I'm trying to inspire you to believe bigger. This is how I keep myself afloat—testimonies and Kenneth Hagin's books.

00:27:39.216 --> 00:28:26.310
Faith comes by hearing. We have challenges, but God is faithful. We live by faith, selling on eBay and Poshmark.

00:28:26.311 --> 00:28:45.634
Here is a testimony from a brother who had a visitation from Jesus.

00:28:45.635 --> 00:30:17.707
He was praying at his kitchen table and saw a vision of himself in a field.

00:30:17.708 --> 00:30:49.237
The Lord walked up and said, 'Come on, get up; it's time to work.'He wore simple white robes and had dark skin, long hair, and a dark beard.

00:30:49.238 --> 00:33:03.425
They walked through hills of cattle, and the Lord said, 'I need a cowboy.'The brother said, 'You've got one, Lord.'The Lord said, 'A cowboy needs a horse,'and the brother replied, 'Even a string of horses, Lord.'It made Him smile.

00:33:03.426 --> 00:34:19.711
Jesus communicates as a friend. If you don't know Him, this is your last call.

00:34:19.712 --> 00:36:22.616
Will you bow your knee today? No sin is too big for Jesus to forgive.

00:36:22.617 --> 00:36:33.851
Say this prayer: 'Jesus, I'm a sinner. Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:36:33.852 --> 00:36:45.365
I believe You are the Son of God. Forgive me of my sins. I want to come home.

00:36:45.366 --> 00:37:54.220
Thank You for setting me free from sin, sickness, and disease.'Now, find a Bible and a good church. Let's believe for your miracle now.

00:37:54.221 --> 00:39:58.879
Father, in the name of Jesus, I believe they are healed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:39:58.880 --> 00:40:08.435
Cancer, go now. Diabetes, go now. We call for new organs, restored eyesight, and hearing.

00:40:08.436 --> 00:40:12.465
I call for healing from strokes. We command tumors to shrivel and go.

00:40:12.466 --> 00:40:15.875
I thank You for restoration in the colon, stomach, and thyroid.

00:40:15.876 --> 00:40:19.075
I call for healing of the prostate, ovaries, and uterus. No more miscarriages.

00:40:19.076 --> 00:43:46.056
We call the wayward children home. I curse breast cancer; go now in Jesus'name.

00:43:46.057 --> 00:45:00.675
I call for healing of throat cancers and gum disease. I command Celiac disease to be healed.

00:45:00.677 --> 00:45:30.409
I thank You for restoring marriages. We believe for financial breakthroughs and creative ideas.

00:45:30.410 --> 00:46:18.912
Thank You, Father. Amen. Please subscribe to our channel. We're going back to the basics—teaching prayer.

00:46:18.913 --> 00:47:45.650
Remember Billie Brim's conference is October 16th to 21st in Branson. It will be a blessing. God bless you all. Jesus loves you.

